<div id='step-203'>
    <h2 class="text-center"><%=Step.find_by(lesson: @lesson, id: @target).name%></h2>
    <h3 id="step-error" class="text-center errors-content"></h3>
    <div class="header text-center">
    Welcome to <em>Finding Pairs</em>! 
    In this game, you will be shown three sets of two graphs with various representations.
    Your goal is to determine whether the two graphs are exactly the same.
    You will have ten seconds to view each pair of graphs.
    If you believe the two representations are of the same graph, press "Same", otherwise press "Different".
    Once you have done all three sets, your score will be presented. You need to get all three correct to pass.
    </div>
    <div class="row empty"></div>
    <div id="error">
    </div>
    <%= button_tag "Begin", type: "button", class: "col-xs-12 btn btn-primary", id: "begin-button"%>
    <div id="timer">
        <div class="col-xs-10"></div>
        <div class="col-xs-2 header" id="timer-field">10</div>
    </div>
    <div id='answer-1'>
        <div class="col-xs-3"></div>
        <div class="col-xs-3"><%= image_tag Image.find(66).image.url, style: "width: 100%"%></div>
        <div class="matrix col-xs-3">
                <div class="bracket">[</div>
                <div class="matrix-content" style="width: 112px">
                    <div class="content-row">
                        <div class="matrix-object">0</div>
                        <div class="matrix-object">0</div>
